{"tid":242891,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺某部分人覺得自己唔睇電視就好威威其實好撚on9","createTime":"2017-05-14T09:00:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T10:07:04.000Z","uid":1627,"like":45,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1d3130e647f67655e93c3296ebc452f56e9f41b","tid":242891,"uid":1627,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T09:00:23.000Z","msg":"總有部分人一知你睇電視(唔止cctvb)就會話：<br />\n吓？而家仲有人睇電視既咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我屋企部電視唔知幾耐冇開過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩年代，你仲睇緊電視？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢種人覺得自己唔睇電視就高人一等，好撚優越，而家開部電視睇下都要畀你地恥笑，乜道理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef5332c78ba89aef3cc38c1b55f7f055a7d285e6","tid":242891,"uid":38944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T09:01:44.000Z","msg":"唔少frd都係咁, 成日覺得佢地咁樣好撚煩同on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877807f0c202f00acbcc4ee1ab5d3a80be8ac1f9","tid":242891,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T09:03:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔少frd都係咁, 成日覺得佢地咁樣好撚煩同on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢種人以為自己唔睇電視就好威威好in，其實更多既只係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：非指所有唔睇電視既人，而係指唔睇電視但同一時間又要恥笑人睇電視既on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84397d443ddb0c249b760f2a3a21c139551b9b99","tid":242891,"uid":1627,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T09:07:19.000Z","msg":"畀負