lockquote><br />\n電視都未被淘汰咁睇電視又會有乜出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8539acf8d70fbe1bce4bc017459a080b38990a","tid":242891,"uid":63912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:02:50.000Z","msg":"人地睇唔睇都唔關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：少開 會聽電視"},{"pid":"f8c3b62e48617972b926787520665de2ad13e86c","tid":242891,"uid":58583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:05:50.000Z","msg":"唔威<br />\n<br />\n但實質上而家睇電視真係好悶<br />\n<br />\n又要比人餵<br />\n<br />\n自己上網想睇咩就睇咩"},{"pid":"a2bdc759ce59faad38262ae2c2e8e14317697455","tid":242891,"uid":1627,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:08:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地睇唔睇都唔關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：少開 會聽電視</blockquote><br />\n人地睇唔睇的確唔關我事，但佢地唔睇得黎又會串埋我睇電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69e869ff0eb29b2732aeaae0805b6ef264c0978","tid":242891,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:09:00.000Z","msg":"有28個串人睇電視既連登仔畀左負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb31f740032689efdcb83bab81e92e0cba2d82a2","tid":242891,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:27:53.000Z","msg":"點解要睇電視？<br />\n呢個世界仲痛咁多好野睇點解你唔睇？"},{"pid":"2c28bb271b26645f5cc4ccc036b207b05ec21065","tid":242891,"uid":33176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"唔係睇電視低質<br />\n係電視台為咗攞rating拖低節目質素黎滿足班屋邨師奶，低學歷廢中，毛都未生齊嘅𡃁仔而放棄一群要求比較高嘅觀眾<br />\n個問題應該係點解要一班要求比較高嘅觀眾遷就電視台去降格睇啲低質節目<br />\nPS：睇明珠台／viutvsix果班除外"}]}